---

Reference mastering (engine/src/mastering.rs) is an independent, clean-room
implementation inspired by Matchering 2.0 (https://github.com/sergree/matchering,
GPL-3.0). It was written from the publicly documented algorithm description
only and contains no Matchering source code; see the "Acknowledgements &
licenses" section of the README for details and the third-party components
bundled with the app.
